# side-by-side render: same snapshot, colored by each classification
write_dump all image cna-hot.png v_iscna type adiam 2.6     view 60 30 zoom 1.2 size 800 800 box yes 0.02     shiny 0.2 ssao yes 4539 0.6 fsaa yes     modify backcolor white boxcolor midnightblue     amap 0.0 1.0 ca 0.0 2 min firebrick max steelblue
